snippet.title: MXGP 24: The Official Game | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
After a 3-year break, the official game of the MXGP is back. Experience the full 2024 MXGP championship with its 20 official tracks and over 50 MX1/MX2 riders. Immerse yourself in the MXGP with a full and deep career mode.

MXGP 24 will be available on November 28th on PC, PS5 and Xbox Series X|S.
